data.description: Introducing 11705 Kingsmill Ct. – Your Dream Home in Waldorf, MD! Nestled in the desirable Sheffield subdivision of Waldorf, this charming and move-in ready home is ready to welcome you with open arms. The home boasts 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms over 2,800 Square feet, so there's plenty of space for your family to grow and thrive.  Step inside and discover the heartwarming ambiance created by a gas fireplace, perfect for cozying up on those cold winter nights. The open and inviting living spaces make hosting friends and family a breeze. Your gourmet kitchen shines with brand new granite countertops, making meal prep a pleasure. But the magic of this home doesn't stop there. The finished basement is an entertainer's dream, providing additional living space and a stylish built-in entertainment center to keep everyone entertained. There's even a lower-level bathroom that's been beautifully renovated for your convenience.  As you step outside, you'll be delighted by the ample patio space, perfect for summer barbecues and al fresco dining. The lush green lawn is equipped with a state-of-the-art sprinkler system, ensuring your garden stays vibrant year-round. Privacy is paramount, thanks to the newly fenced backyard, allowing your children and pets to play freely. And let's not forget the brand new HVAC system, ensuring your comfort all year round while also saving on energy costs. If you need some relaxation, the primary bathroom has been thoughtfully renovated to provide you with a spa-like experience. After a long day, you can unwind in the luxurious bathtub or enjoy the separate shower.  Don't miss the opportunity to make 11705 Kingsmill Ct. your forever home. With all these fantastic updates and amenities, this Waldorf gem is sure to go fast. Schedule your viewing today and get ready to make cherished memories in this wonderful family home.
